# ==============================================================================
# AETHERFORGE SECURE .GITIGNORE
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. SENSITIVE DATA & SECRETS (NEVER COMMIT)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# These files often contain API keys, passwords, or private configuration data.
.env
.env.*
*.env
secrets.json
config.json
credentials.json
auth.json
*.pem
*.key
*.cert
*.pfx
*.p12
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. MARKDOWN & DOCUMENTATION (WHITELIST APPROACH)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore all markdown files to prevent accidental leakage of sensitive notes.
*.md
*.markdown
*.mdx

# ...EXCEPT for these explicitly whitelisted public files.
!README.md
!PROJECTGUIDELINES.md
!ROADMAP.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CHANGELOG.md

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. PYTHON ENVIRONMENTS & CACHES
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents massive directories and compiled bytecode from bloating the repo.
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env_aether/
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. LOGS & TELEMETRY
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Log files can inadvertently capture sensitive system states or prompt data.
*.log
logs/
telemetry/
.npm/_logs/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. ML MODELS & LARGE BINARIES
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents checking in 30GB GGUF models or database files.
*.gguf
*.bin
*.pt
*.safetensors
models/
checkpoints/
*.sqlite3
*.db

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. IDE & SYSTEM FILES
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents local machine configurations from causing merge conflicts.
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db